<section sectnbr = "1H">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "08">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "4">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A1804002" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Ignition Spark Test
</title>
<attention1>
<ptxt>
If this test is performed without disconnecting the injector connectors, a spark from a plug may ignite fuel vapor coming out of the spark plug holes during the test, causing a fire or explosion.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Be sure to disconnect the injector connectors from the injectors before performing this test.
</ptxt>
</attention1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove spark plugs. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1806001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Inspect spark plugs. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1806002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect all fuel injector connectors.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect ignition coil connector (1) to ignition coil assembly (3).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect spark plug (2) to ignition coil assembly, and ground spark plug.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP60B180004.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "63.912mm" ver = "01" gw = "211" gh = "165"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Crank engine and check if each spark plug sparks.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
If no spark is emitted, inspect the related parts. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A1804001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
